# adventofcode
Solving http://adventofcode.com puzzles using Node v7.2.

To run one day/part
------
`npm start <year#> <day#> <part#>`

Example
-------
```
npm start 2016 1 1
1.1 running...
1.1 answer:	   543903
1.1 time:	   00:09:7400
```

To test all days in a year
-----------
`npm run 2016-test`
